buildPlayground() - Method in class Model.Playground.EnemyPlayground
Restriction: You can only build the Playground if all Ships are created and the placement of the ships are valid Creates the Playground, as it is the enemy playground, all Fields are filled with Water Objects
buildPlayground() - Method in interface Model.Playground.IPlayground
This method builds the Playground, if there are no Ships in the ShipList, it will create an playground filled all Fields with water If there are Ships in the List it will place them as shipParts Creates the Playground, sets all ships-parts on the Field (if it is the own Field) and fills the rest of the fields with water
